  "markdown": "**Marine Life 2030 Logo Usage Policy** : The Marine Life 2030 logo is intended to be used by approved partners, for informational and promotional purposes in support of the programme. Please email [[email protected]](/cdn-cgi/l/email-protection#1b767a6972757e77727d7e292b282b5b7c767a727735787476) to request approval to use, and to receive high resolution versions of, the logo. Review the Logo Use & Style Guide (linked to the left) for appropriate usage guidelines. Unauthorized use of the logo is strongly discouraged; please notify [[email protected]](/cdn-cgi/l/email-protection#b1dcd0c3d8dfd4ddd8d7d483818281f1d6dcd0d8dd9fd2dedc) of any unauthorized usages of the logo.\n\nPantone 7555\n\n#D09E11\n\nR: 208 G: 157 B: 017\n\nPantone 3035\n\n#004153\n\nR: 001 G: 062 B: 082\n\nPantone 631\n\n#2CB6CE\n\nR: 006 G: 175 B: 196",
